    "portability": "R9700's window win is on a different (ROCm) attention backend \u2014 does not transfer to FlashInfer.",
    "upstream": "issue-worthy: flag validates at arg-parse, sets draft layers, then asserts at boot"
  },
  "verdict": {
    "memory": "WIN \u2014 pool-cap frees the profiler over-provision (4.3x at 98K/0.80); spec+graphs boot at every CTX incl. full 256K",
