    "receipt_correction": "the v0.5.12 '1.65x @16K' was delta-method with unverified depth; server-verified: spec loses by 13.8K actual",
    "task17_implication": "the dynamic fallback threshold is a DEPTH crossover (~8-10K), not a VRAM band; only ~2.7% of SWE-bench prompts sit under it -> EAGLE3 stays off the mission workload; NGRAM remains the depth spec"
